  "description": "Adds culling to leaf blocks, providing a huge performance boost over vanilla.",
  "body": "<center><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Adds culling to leaf blocks, providing a huge performance boost over vanilla.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">This is a recreation of the OptiFine feature 'Smart Leaves'</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Yes, it's that simple.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">This mod can also be used to increase framerates with my <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/texture-packs/motschens-better-leaves\">Better Leaves Resourcepack</a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Completely compatible with Sodium, Canvas, LambaBetterGrass, etc.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/LzFXtm8/Oak-Leaves-JE4-1.png\" width=\"768\" height=\"132\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/U55i4uD.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"655\" height=\"368\" /></p>",
